#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Battle"
msgid ""
"Sentries now patrol Death Mountain to\n"
"eliminate intruders.\n"
"\n"
"Avoid their notice as you lead Yunobo to the\n"
"<1.se_co>cannons<2.re_co> to drive Divine Beast Vah Rudania\n"
"into the crater."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_BattlePlaying"
msgid ""
"Thanks to Yunobo using Daruk's Protection\n"
"to act as your cannonball, you drove\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Rudania into the crater!\n"
"\n"
"It is time to enter <1.se_co>Divine Beast Vah Rudania<2.re_co>\n"
"and bring it to a halt."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Bridge"
msgid ""
"Yunobo used Daruk's Protection to\n"
"act as a cannonball. The Bridge of Eldin\n"
"has been lowered! \n"
"\n"
"All you need to do now is to cross\n"
"the <1.se_co>Bridge of Eldin<2.re_co> and drive\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Rudania into\n"
"the crater."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Desc"
msgid ""
"Bludo, Boss of Goron City, wants to challenge\n"
"the marauding Divine Beast Vah Rudania,\n"
"but his backache is too severe.\n"
"\n"
"What's worse, Yunobo has yet to return from\n"
"the <1.se_co>Abandoned North Mine <2.re_co>with the painkillers\n"
"he was sent to fetch."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Dungeon"
msgid ""
"Defeating Fireblight Ganon freed the spirit of\n"
"Daruk, Champion of the Goron race. He has\n"
"piloted the Divine Beast to the summit of\n"
"Death Mountain in preparation for the assault\n"
"on Ganon.\n"
"\n"
"Seeing this, a relieved Yunobo returned to his\n"
"home in Goron City. You should go there and\n"
"tell <1.se_co>Bludo <2.re_co>all that has happened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Finished"
msgid ""
"You reported your success in restoring the\n"
"Divine Beast Vah Rudania to its true self.\n"
"Peace has finally returned to Goron City.\n"
"\n"
"In addition, you received the Champion Daruk's\n"
"might and can now use Daruk's Protection."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_GoDeathMt"
msgid ""
"You helped Yunobo fend off monsters at the\n"
"Bridge of Eldin before telling him that Bludo's\n"
"plan had been called off.\n"
"\n"
"You still need to get inside the Divine Beast\n"
"somehow, though... The best way forward may\n"
"be to lower the <1.se_co>Bridge of Eldin<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_GoGoronCity"
msgid ""
"Bludo thanked you for helping Yunobo.\n"
"After taking the painkillers, Bludo was about\n"
"to go challenge Divine Beast Vah Rudania,\n"
"but then his back started hurting again.\n"
"No one will be challenging the Divine Beast\n"
"today, it seems.\n"
"\n"
"Yunobo has already gone ahead to the\n"
"<1.se_co>Bridge of Eldin<2.re_co>, so you must meet him there\n"
"to let him know about this change of plans."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Name"
msgid "Divine Beast Vah Rudania"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_NorthMine"
msgid ""
"You met Drak in the Abandoned North Mine,\n"
"who told you that Yunobo left for the vault\n"
"deep in its reaches. That's the last anyone\n"
"has seen of Yunobo...\n"
"\n"
"Mount a search operation for Yunobo, who was\n"
"headed for the <1.se_co>vault<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Fire_Relic_Storage"
msgid ""
"You met Yunobo in the Abandoned North Mine.\n"
"\n"
"Yunobo hurried back to Goron City to deliver\n"
"the painkillers Bludo needs for his backache.\n"
"\n"
"You should go speak to <1.se_co>Bludo<2.re_co> to collect\n"
"your reward."
msgstr ""

